  <title>WebKit2.EDITING_COMMAND_SELECT_ALL</title>
  <p>The select all command. Selects all the content of the current text field in
a <link xref="WebKit2.WebView"/>.
It is always possible to select all text, no matter whether the
<link xref="WebKit2.WebView"/> content is editable or not. You can still check it
with <link xref="WebKit2.WebView.can_execute_editing_command"/>.</p>

